%% Insight-to-action flow. See 08-operational-intelligence.md
flowchart TB
  Snapshot[verified data snapshot\nroutes / AI budget / overdue reminders] --> Gen[read-only generators]
  Gen --> Insights[Insights w/ evidence + confidence + recommendedAction]
  Insights --> Prioritize[prioritize: severity > confidence > $impact]
  Prioritize --> Flag{INSIGHTS_UI_ENABLED?}
  Flag -- off --> None[nothing surfaced]
  Flag -- on --> Surface[owner-facing insight cards]
  Surface --> Worker[eligible AI worker]
  Worker --> Approval[approval queue if Level 3+]
  Approval --> Act[human-approved action]
